                       @{bg fill}@{fg shine}@{B}The AMIGA Handler Guide@{UB}@{fg text}@{bg back}


V1.1.2             Release: 34          Date: Germany, Berlin, 26.03.2000
___________________________________________________________________________________

@{U}Based on an idea by @{"Heiko Schr÷der" link Authors}, Author of @{I}LibsGuide@{UU}@{UI}, @{I}DevsGuide@{UI} and @{I}DTypesGuide@{UI}.
___________________________________________________________________________________

                                  @{U}@{B}First steps:@{UU}@{UB}

   First: @{"Heiko Schr÷der" link Authors} creates @{I}LibsGuide@{UI}, @{I}DevsGuide@{UI} and @{I}DTypesGuide@{UI}.
  Second: @{"Stuart Kelly  " link Authors} creates @{I}ClassesGuide@{UI}
21.04.99: @{"Michaela Pr³▀ " link Authors} begin the @{I}HandlerGuide@{UI}
08.03.00: @{"Michaela Pr³▀ " link Authors} first use @{I}VersCheck V3@{UI} (beta)
@{U}                                                                                   @{UU}

                             @{U}@{B}Words about this Guide@{UU}@{UB}

This guide is an informationsystem. You find information about the latest known
versions and the authors. You also find, if I know important or additional
informations. But you find nothing about contents, use or installing of them.
___________________________________________________________________________________

                            @{U}@{B}HandlerGuide Contents@{UU}@{UB}

  @{" List of handler           " link Handler}

  @{" Contact the guide authors " link Authors}

  @{" Your input for this guide " link Register}

___________________________________________________________________________________

This guide is completly created @{I}GuidEd@{UI}, written and copyright by @{U}Linus McCabe@{UU}, a
MUI based AmigaGuide editor. Take a look for it in the Aminet.

The version compare uses @{I}VersCheck@{UI}, a freeware program, written by myself. You find latest version on my @{"homepage" link Authors} or in the Aminet. 

@{B}Michaela Pr³▀@{UB}
@{B}Berlin - Germany@{UB}

